{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "wati-otp-collection",
    "name": "WhatsApp OTP (WATI) Authentication",
    "description": "WhatsApp OTP login flow using WATI API",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Send OTP to WhatsApp",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
              "  var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "  pm.environment.set('otp_sid', jsonData.data.sid);",
              "  pm.environment.set('otp_code', jsonData.data.otp);",
              "  pm.environment.set('phone', pm.request.body.raw);",
              "  console.log('✅ OTP sent! Check your WhatsApp');",
              "  console.log('OTP Code (dev only): ' + jsonData.data.otp);",
              "}"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\"phone\": \"919876543210\"}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/send-otp",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "api",
            "auth",
            "send-otp"
          ]
        },
        "description": "Sends OTP to user's WhatsApp\n\n**Phone Format:**\n- `919876543210` (with country code)\n- `+919876543210` (with + prefix)\n\n**Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"status\": \"success\",\n  \"message\": \"OTP sent successfully via WhatsApp\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"phone\": \"919876543210\",\n    \"sid\": \"wati-1234567890\",\n    \"expiresIn\": \"5 minutes\",\n    \"otp\": \"123456\"  // Dev only\n  }\n}\n```"
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Verify OTP Code",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
              "  var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "  if (jsonData.data.verified) {",
              "    pm.environment.set('otp_verified', 'true');",
              "    console.log('✅ OTP Verified! User can now login');",
              "  }",
              "} else {",
              "  console.log('❌ OTP verification failed');",
              "}"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\"phone\": \"919876543210\", \"code\": \"{{otp_code}}\"}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/verify-otp",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "api",
            "auth",
            "verify-otp"
          ]
        },
        "description": "Verifies OTP code sent to WhatsApp\n\n**Request:**\n- `phone`: Phone number (same as send-otp)\n- `code`: OTP code received on WhatsApp\n\n**Response:**\n```json\n{\n  \"status\": \"success\",\n  \"message\": \"OTP verified successfully\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"verified\": true\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Failure Cases:**\n- Invalid OTP: \"Invalid OTP. 2 attempts remaining.\"\n- Expired: \"OTP has expired. Please request a new one.\"\n- Too many attempts: \"Too many failed attempts. Please request a new OTP.\""
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "3. Manual Test - Replace OTP in Request",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\"phone\": \"919876543210\", \"code\": \"PASTE_OTP_HERE\"}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/verify-otp",
          "host": [
            "{{baseUrl}}"
          ],
          "path": [
            "api",
            "auth",
            "verify-otp"
          ]
        },
        "description": "Use this when you want to manually enter the OTP code\n\n1. First request: \"1. Send OTP to WhatsApp\"\n2. Check your WhatsApp for OTP\n3. Copy the OTP code\n4. Replace `PASTE_OTP_HERE` with the code\n5. Send this request"
      }
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "phone",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "otp_code",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "otp_sid",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "otp_verified",
      "value": "false",
      "type": "boolean"
    }
  ]
}
